00:19:01.300 --> 00:19:03.800 align:middle line:90%
And I drove her to the hospital.

00:19:03.800 --> 00:19:07.150 align:middle line:84%
She died in the car, in the
ambulance a couple of times.

00:19:07.150 --> 00:19:09.670 align:middle line:84%
We eventually got an
ambulance and was resuscitated

00:19:09.670 --> 00:19:11.470 align:middle line:90%
and then went into a coma.

00:19:11.470 --> 00:19:13.840 align:middle line:84%
And my initial reaction
to all of that--

00:19:13.840 --> 00:19:16.690 align:middle line:84%
because I had been trained
in a lot of shamanic healing,

00:19:16.690 --> 00:19:18.220 align:middle line:84%
and it was just a
gut reaction-- was

00:19:18.220 --> 00:19:22.959 align:middle line:84%
to grab her and hang onto her
with everything that I had.

00:19:22.959 --> 00:19:23.875 align:middle line:90%
And that's what I did.

00:19:23.875 --> 00:19:25.450 align:middle line:84%
I just didn't want
to let her go.

00:19:25.450 --> 00:19:28.510 align:middle line:90%


00:19:28.510 --> 00:19:30.250 align:middle line:84%
And she was in a
coma for five weeks.

00:19:30.250 --> 00:19:32.040 align:middle line:90%
And we waited, and we prayed.

00:19:32.040 --> 00:19:32.840 align:middle line:90%
And we waited.

00:19:32.840 --> 00:19:37.450 align:middle line:90%


00:19:37.450 --> 00:19:40.021 align:middle line:84%
And then the
hospital chaplain had

00:19:40.021 --> 00:19:42.520 align:middle line:84%
came and said that we needed
to take her off the respirator,

00:19:42.520 --> 00:19:44.800 align:middle line:84%
that she wasn't going to come
to, that 80% of her brain

00:19:44.800 --> 00:19:45.966 align:middle line:90%
had been flooded with blood.

00:19:45.966 --> 00:19:49.780 align:middle line:84%
So even if she, did she would
be incapable of doing anything.

00:19:49.780 --> 00:19:53.410 align:middle line:84%
And I went out and sat in
the local park and meditated.

00:19:53.410 --> 00:19:55.870 align:middle line:84%
And I had this very strong
sense the whole time

00:19:55.870 --> 00:19:57.790 align:middle line:90%
of being connected to Katherine.

00:19:57.790 --> 00:19:59.274 align:middle line:90%
And I saw her in my mind's eye.

00:19:59.274 --> 00:20:00.940 align:middle line:84%
And I said to her,
they want to turn off

00:20:00.940 --> 00:20:02.023 align:middle line:90%
the respirator, Katherine.

00:20:02.023 --> 00:20:03.320 align:middle line:90%
What do you want to do?

00:20:03.320 --> 00:20:06.820 align:middle line:90%
And she said, give me 24 hours.

00:20:06.820 --> 00:20:09.370 align:middle line:84%
So I told her
husband, Roger, this.

00:20:09.370 --> 00:20:12.228 align:middle line:84%
And he told the chaplain
we need 24 hours set aside.

00:20:12.228 --> 00:20:14.269 align:middle line:84%
And the next day, Katherine
came out of the coma.

00:20:14.269 --> 00:20:19.260 align:middle line:90%


00:20:19.260 --> 00:20:21.090 align:middle line:84%
So when she came
out of the coma,

00:20:21.090 --> 00:20:24.540 align:middle line:84%
there was a moment of thinking,
everything was exactly

00:20:24.540 --> 00:20:26.640 align:middle line:84%
as it had been,
that she was going

00:20:26.640 --> 00:20:30.060 align:middle line:84%
to be 100% who she had been
in every way, shape, and form.

00:20:30.060 --> 00:20:32.064 align:middle line:84%
And of course, when they
took the respirator out

00:20:32.064 --> 00:20:33.480 align:middle line:84%
and she could
speak, we discovered

00:20:33.480 --> 00:20:35.760 align:middle line:84%
