a toothbrush or a spoon.

00:20:43.770 --> 00:20:46.410 align:middle line:84%
And she's had a
very long struggle

00:20:46.410 --> 00:20:51.120 align:middle line:84%
of patching together her memory
of learning to walk again.

00:20:51.120 --> 00:20:54.560 align:middle line:90%
