00:20:54.560 --> 00:20:57.590 align:middle line:84%
I certainly had an enormous
amount of ambivalence

00:20:57.590 --> 00:21:00.530 align:middle line:84%
about whether I had done
Katharine any favor.

00:21:00.530 --> 00:21:02.810 align:middle line:84%
The doctors were very
clear that had she

00:21:02.810 --> 00:21:04.790 align:middle line:84%
been on the road,
which was where

00:21:04.790 --> 00:21:07.580 align:middle line:84%
she was headed or whatnot,
that she would have died--

00:21:07.580 --> 00:21:12.200 align:middle line:84%
that given the circumstances
of the moment and my being

00:21:12.200 --> 00:21:14.390 align:middle line:84%
there, that that was
why she had lived.

00:21:14.390 --> 00:21:16.610 align:middle line:84%
Watching her struggle, I
had incredible ambivalence

00:21:16.610 --> 00:21:18.620 align:middle line:84%
about whether I had
done her any favor.

00:21:18.620 --> 00:21:20.060 align:middle line:90%
She's very clear.

00:21:20.060 --> 00:21:22.790 align:middle line:84%
She is happy for every
day that she's alive.

00:21:22.790 --> 00:21:25.380 align:middle line:84%
And she's very clear that
she chose to be alive.

00:21:25.380 --> 00:21:28.490 align:middle line:84%
She has very clear memories
of those conversations

00:21:28.490 --> 00:21:31.410 align:middle line:84%
we had when she was in a coma
and I would meditate and speak

00:21:31.410 --> 00:21:32.210 align:middle line:90%
to her.

00:21:32.210 --> 00:21:35.870 align:middle line:84%
That she remembers
clear as a bell.

00:21:35.870 --> 00:21:39.470 align:middle line:84%
Being with Katherine when she
went through the brain aneurysm

00:21:39.470 --> 00:21:42.110 align:middle line:90%
was a kind of abrupt awakening.

00:21:42.110 --> 00:21:44.180 align:middle line:84%
When someone close
to you or you has

00:21:44.180 --> 00:21:48.110 align:middle line:84%
a very close call with death
or gets a fatal prognosis,

00:21:48.110 --> 00:21:51.950 align:middle line:84%
it's a reminder of
what we don't know.

00:21:51.950 --> 00:21:54.350 align:middle line:84%
I don't know if this is my
last 30 seconds before a brain

00:21:54.350 --> 00:21:55.840 align:middle line:90%
aneurysm burst for me.

00:21:55.840 --> 00:21:56.640 align:middle line:90%
I have no idea.

00:21:56.640 --> 00:21:57.170 align:middle line:90%
We didn't know.

00:21:57.170 --> 00:21:59.450 align:middle line:84%
Katherine and I were standing
in the kitchen chatting.

00:21:59.450 --> 00:22:02.330 align:middle line:84%
Everything was the way
it had been for years.

00:22:02.330 --> 00:22:04.460 align:middle line:90%
There's no way to know.

00:22:04.460 --> 00:22:06.800 align:middle line:84%
And so to live your
life fully-- and also

00:22:06.800 --> 00:22:09.110 align:middle line:90%
that there are no deals.

00:22:09.110 --> 00:22:11.310 align:middle line:84%
A number of people
said to me, well,

00:22:11.310 --> 00:22:14.090 align:middle line:84%
what do you think Katherine
did that brought this

00:22:14.090 --> 00:22:15.930 align:middle line:90%
into her life?

00:22:15.930 --> 00:22:20.120 align:middle line:84%
And I just want to say,
that's a crazy kind of notion.

00:22:20.120 --> 00:22:22.550 align:middle line:84%
We can't possibly
know what causes

00:22:22.550 --> 00:22:25.220 align:middle line:84%
something like this, whether
purely physical or otherwise.

00:22:25.220 --> 00:22:27.660 align:middle line:84%
We can say what we've
learned from it.

00:22:27.660 --> 00:22:30.050 align:middle line:84%
And what I've learned is
that there are no deals.

00:22:30.050 --> 00:22:32.810 align:middle line:84%
If you are doing spiritual
work, a spiritual practice

00:22:32.810 --> 00:22:35.960 align:middle line:84%
in the hopes that the universe
will reward you with safety

00:22:35.960 --> 00:22:39.480 align:middle line:90%
from tragedy, it's an illusion.

00:22:39.480 --> 00:22:40.760 align:middle line:90%
It's a fantasy.

00:22:40.760 --> 00:22:42.905 align:middle line:90%
Life includes suffering.

00:22:42.905 --> 00:22:45.950 align:middle line:90%
It includes unexpected tragedy.

00:22:45.950 --> 00:22:48.650 align:middle line:84%
And what a spiritual
practice and path does

00:22:48.650 --> 00:22:52.490 align:middle line:84%
is help you expand
and hold all of it.

00:22:52.490 --> 00:22:54.500 align:middle line:84%
But you don't miss
parts of it then.

00:22:54.500 --> 00:22:58.300 align:middle line:84%
You don't get exempted from
certain personal tragedies.

00:22:58.300 --> 00:23:00.760 align:middle line:84%
That's still going to come to
you like it does to everyone.

